    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289076</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……今の……
無理して戦わなくても、
逃げられたんじゃ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just now...wasn't that fight
kinda silly? I mean we could
have just walked past him.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>先手必勝。
先にぶっ叩いた方が勝ちかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The early bird gets the worm!
Attack before they can make
a move and you'll win!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>にしては、ダオスに対しては
ずいぶん、おくてだな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That pretty much sums up
how Dhaos's plans worked.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それはあいつの方だよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's the way he chose to do things.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あのバカ……私が近づくたびに、
あちこち飛ばしてくれちゃって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That idiot... Each and every time
I get close to him, he sends me
to a different timeline.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289628</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレには&lt;Rody&gt;がダオスと
会わずにすんで、ほっと
してるふうにも見えるぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think it's a relief you didn't
have to meet the guy in 
person, all things considered.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……かもね。
怖い相手と戦わずに
済んでほっとしてんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Maybe. I was afraid of getting
dragged into a fight with him
back then. I'm relieved about that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふーん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hmmm...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、それでも君は
ダオスを追っているんだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And yet you insist on chasing
after Dhaos. Why?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289968</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……心残りなんだよ、まだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...There's an ache in my
heart I can't get rid of.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>英雄になりそこねたからか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is it because you want to become a hero?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ま、そういうことかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, I guess that could be it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『英雄』か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A hero, huh...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>少なくとも今の僕は、
そんな立派なものじゃないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nowadays I've learned the title
isn't all it's cracked up to be.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>世界を守りたいって気持ちも
もちろんあった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sure, we protected the world.
That is a certainty.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、僕を突き動かしてたのは
ただの復讐心だったんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, when I try to pin down a motive for
why I did the things I did...it all boils
down to wanting revenge for my parents.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290536</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私も……
&lt;Cless&gt;さんと同じです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I feel the same as &lt;Cless&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290536</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私も……母を
ダオスに殺された
のですから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>After all, it was due to Dhaos that
my dear mother got slaughtered.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『英雄』とか『時空戦士』とか
そんな呼び名が時々、重荷なんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Being called a "Hero" or a
"Hero of Time" can sometimes
be a heavy burden to carry.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、僕たちは、
みんなのその呼び声に
応えなくちゃいけない……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And yet, people throw these words
around so easily. Even when we
don't live up to their expectations...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290836</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、利用されてんの知ってて
騎士団を手伝ってんのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that why you offered to
help the Imperial Knights?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>利用しているのは、
僕も同じだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I offer my help since I'm
no different from them.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>290988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さんも？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're the same as them?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>僕は『英雄』と呼ばれるに
ふさわしい自分になるため、
彼らを利用してる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I felt a need to justify being called a
"hero" of any sort. To live up to that
duty I have to help those in need.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>TL checkchanged feeling to duty but we arent sure</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291168</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291324</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まったく、&lt;Cless&gt;も&lt;Mint&gt;も
真面目すぎるぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Damn, you two sure beat yourselves
up over things you can't help, huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291324</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>期待したい奴には勝手に
させとけばいいんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't put yourself through hell just 'cuz
others expect too much from you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291452</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレ……&lt;Cless&gt;さんも
&lt;Mint&gt;さんもがんばって
『英雄』やらなくてもいいと思う</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think that...it's okay, since
Mister &lt;Cless&gt; and Miss &lt;Mint&gt; are
trying hard to be "heroes."</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いや、違うかな……
今のふたりが、
嘘かマジかわかんねし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, that came out wrong...
It'd be a lie if I just said you
were like I expected you to be.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……でも、なんか
あんまがんばんなくても、
ふたりはその……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, you're trying your best! So
if you keep trying, you'll...um...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……あぁっ！
なんかうまく言えねー！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gah! This is really hard to say!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;は自然体のままの
ふたりでも十分魅力的って
言いたいんだよね？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think &lt;Dio&gt;'s trying to say in his
own way, both of you are amazing
people as is. Right, &lt;Dio&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>291992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うぉっ……
今のでわかったのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Woah... She picked up that mess pretty well.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしも……そう思います</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I feel the same as &lt;Dio&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だって、&lt;Red&gt;トーティス村&lt;White&gt;の
皆さん、おふたりのこと
大好きみたいでしたから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think that's why everyone
in &lt;Red&gt;Totus&lt;White&gt; loves you two!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ま、なんにしてもだ。
ふたりとも片意地
張りすぎなんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, even telling you this, you'll
still act stubborn, won't you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなに難しく
考えなくたって
いいと思うぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just stop thinking so hard about
things we can't change, okay?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君はちょい難しく
考えたほうがいいんじゃない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's quite a fitting comment coming
from our thoughtful &lt;Chester&gt;, amiright?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>39</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_047&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どういう意味だよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's that supposed to mean!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292620</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_048&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ！　オ、オレ、なんか
&lt;Cless&gt;さんに
偉そうなこと言っちゃった？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>U-Um. I'm sorry if I offended
you Mister &lt;Cless&gt;. If I said
anything inappropriate.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_049&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いや、ありがとう、&lt;Dio&gt;。
&lt;Mel&gt;も、それに&lt;Chester&gt;も</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No offense taken. Thank you very much,
&lt;Dio&gt;, &lt;Mel&gt;, and &lt;Chester&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_180_030_050&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さ、先に進もう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now then, let's get a move on.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
